{"tid":1180023,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"OH MY GIRL Arin女大十八變，沒有瀏海完美進化成仙女！","createTime":"2019-05-31T13:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T15:56:37.000Z","uid":231132,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8e4e66e2396afc66625bb9d2fcf77a5db936bc","tid":1180023,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMtst3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMtst3r.jpg&h=fdaa51c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女大真的十八變啊！Arin變超美了！<br />\n女團Oh My Girl的可愛老么Arin在這次回歸實在漂亮太多，昨天（14日）的音樂節目舞台更被韓網友稱為傳奇，清純的美貌令人心動，引起了網友們的熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xw4fCWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxw4fCWV.jpg&h=14b6582a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOh My Girl本月8日以首張正規專輯《The Fifth Season》回歸，成員在主打歌《SSFWL》的舞台上變身優雅的仙子舞動，而隊内的可愛擔當Arin卻轉變成小熟女。換了以往的瀏海髮型和貼雙眼皮膠紙，加上轉換了整體的妝容，舞台最後凝視鏡頭時更讓人一秒錯覺是Suzy。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDh1yve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDh1yve.jpg&h=bae73718&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zoXdpBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzoXdpBV.jpg&h=0b7b4f7d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n網友們都不斷讚嘆：「最近看起來最漂亮了」、「好好長大了，好漂亮」、「真的是清純女神」、「超美啊」等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqFB6QW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqFB6QW.jpg&h=3200326e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67O0O4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67O0O4h.jpg&h=095f45cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWf6KCC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWf6KCC.jpg&h=3b8734af&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDzZ4CD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDzZ4CD.jpg&h=c2477275&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n亦都有人也找出出道初期的Arin對比，果然女大十八變啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkR2hXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkR2hXL.jpg&h=5112fefd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmjvrQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmjvrQ5.jpg&h=1b767b75&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CzUqHQPUAAI_mEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCzUqHQPUAAI_mEU.jpg&h=c99e25bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCA22qp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCA22qp.jpg&h=7081f98f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔點睇❤(ӦｖӦ｡)"},{"pid":"40b51b025c0947d32c4a887b5cdf93f83e0a64ec","tid":1180023,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"屁股蛋❤"},{"pid":"c80ca2850d96eb066b4e9dfec5ff6220051d3bb5","tid":1180023,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"好能靚。。。"},{"pid":"15a2ae3060cf0cc528035bcdac8211d964bc1be8","tid":1180023,"uid":106633,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"整咗就整咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6344c6d973085d9ff1d2efd00f0d79aac327921b","tid":1180023,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"我女友❤"},{"pid":"cc485325a36355a480277360e23548cad05ca31f","tid":1180023,"uid":231132,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a2ae3060cf0cc528035bcdac8211d964bc1be8","tid":1180023,"uid":106633,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"整咗就整咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"減肥就話整咗 有冇咁毒呀你(ー_ー)"},{"pid":"97c5114008d8fbed82e8de033b925fba8fc33fc4","tid":1180023,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit